is uncertain. It was confused with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1895" box="[1099,1249,490,523]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Crocidura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="139" pageNumber="536" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="somalica">C. somalica</taxonomicName>
